    <!-- Rows are stacked in a grouplist so it scrolls to keep the focused
         row visible instead of every row having to be squeezed to fit a
         fixed 1080px-tall screen.

         Every poster/thumb image uses <aspectratio>scale</aspectratio> so
         Jellyfin's real image shapes (portrait 2:3 posters for Movies/
         Series, landscape ~16:9 thumbs for Episodes) crop-to-fill their box
         instead of being stretched/distorted. Recently Added Movies/TV are
         both portrait boxes matching Movie/Series posters, sized the same
         as each other on request. Recently Added TV mixes newly-added
         Series (portrait, native fit) and Episodes (landscape, scale-crops
         to fill the portrait frame). -->
    <control type="grouplist" id="210">
